* Desmonus was about to lift off into the sky and fly back to the Iron Fist 
when something moving off to her right caught her attention and made her 
look.
A colored kitty ( Diana ) was moving through the grasses towards the Maximal 
City.
Meal! was the first thing that came to mind and she started to slither 
towards her.*

******************************

* Tremmer heaved a sigh and put the rackit down, moving out of the way and 
out of the holo room.
There was no point in playing a useless game when he wasn't in the mood for 
it. And besides, he had a feeling that he could be doing something alot more 
important with his time.*
